    "Integrating insights from neuroscience can help improve AI models by grounding them in biological mechanisms.",
    "Collaborative efforts may include using brain imaging data to guide sensory model design, developing algorithms inspired by neural coding, or building adaptive systems that respond to physiological signals.",
    "These directions can support more realistic simulations of taste and smell, and contribute to the creation of more effective and inclusive sensory technologies.",
    "This paper highlights recent progress in the integration of artificial intelligence into olfactory and gustatory research.",
    "AI techniques have significantly improved the efficiency and accuracy of sensory analysis by enabling the interpretation of complex chemical and perceptual data."
